#: ../../T/touristic.rst:5
msgid "touristic"
msgstr "touristic"

#: ../../T/touristic.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../T/touristic.rst:9
msgid ""
"Having the quality of a :ref:`tourist`\\. Often used as a pejorative, as in "
"‘losing touristic scum’. Often spelled ‘turistic’ or ‘turistik’, so that "
"phrase might be more properly rendered ‘lusing turistic scum’."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`tourist`\\ の性質を持つこと。‘losing touristic "
"scum’(負け犬の観光客のクズ)のように、しばしば軽蔑的に使われる。‘turistic’や‘turistik’と綴られることもよくあり、その場合その言い回しは‘lusing"
" turistic scum’とより適切に表されるかもしれない。"
